snippet.title: Sonic Spectre Reveal Trailer - (Sonic Fan Game)
snippet.description:
#sonicthehedgehog #sonicfangames #sonic 
Sonic Spectre is a free 2D Sonic the Hedgehog fan game made by me: TheBearBridge.

SFHQ download Link: 
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-spectre-v0-5-sage-2023-demo.1708/

Gamejolt download link:
https://gamejolt.com/games/sonic-the-hedgehog-spectre/809705

All characters in the trailer are a property of SEGA.

/Music/
Combat Night by MaxieDaMan: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5-nsw0jYNK0
Neon Paradise by MaxieDaMan: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_M5hwUFptDc
Sonic and Knuckles miniboss remix by Bboynoe: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EPGrEpd4o-A&list=PLSJ-n5hOqteQUvQqnCgdAYJUdG0V-fkBX&index=6
Other music owned by SEGA: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8SRIcGsjMDM


Trailer made with Clipchamp
